         MACRO ,
&NM      MAPXCL &DSECT=YES,&PFX=XCL                       ADDED GP15238
.*
.*  MAPPING MACRO FOR EXWCLEAN CHAIN. ELEMENTS ON THIS CHAIN ARE
.*  SERVICED WHEN AN EXHIBIT SESSION TERMINATES (EXHAMODS).
.*  SERVICES INCLUDE FREEMAIN, DASD CLOSE/FREE, ETC.
.*
         LCLC  &P
&P       SETC  'XCL'
         AIF   ('&PFX' EQ '').HAVEP
&P       SETC  '&PFX'
.HAVEP   ANOP  ,
&NM      MACMAPHD MAP,PFX=&PFX,DSECT=&DSECT,DFLT=CLEAN          GP15238
&P.NEXT  DC    A(0)          ADDRESS OF NEXT ENTRY
&P.SPLEN DC    F'0'          SUBPOL/LENGTH OF ENTRY
&P.TYPE  DC    XL1'0'        ENTRY TYPE
&P.NAME  DC    CL3' '        PRIMARY NAME
&P.QUAL  DC    F'0'          OTH. NAME QUALIFIER/DISAMBIGUATION
&P.SIZE  EQU   *-&P.NEXT       HEADER SIZE
&P.USER  DS    0D            START OF USER DATA
.MEND    MEND  ,
